Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:04.36,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Please sit in the waiting room over there, Mrs. Iwakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:07.12,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Lain, there's no need to be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.32,0:00:11.00,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Come, take a seat over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.53,0:00:14.68,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Ah... would you like a juice or something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.50,0:00:18.98,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,If you don't, that's fine as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.65,0:00:20.86,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.09,0:00:26.80,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I'm thirsty, so I'll probably make some black tea. Would you like to join me, Lain?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.29,0:00:30.08,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,It'd be odd if I was the only one with a drink, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.50,0:00:32.36,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.17,0:00:34.57,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,What would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:36.64,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I have all kinds of drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:38.09,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,The same one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.58,0:00:40.02,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,You want tea as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.57,0:00:41.37,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Wonderful,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.75,0:00:43.36,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,give me just a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.25,0:00:47.98,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,You can add sugar and milk as well, if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.60,0:00:49.96,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.13,0:00:55.08,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Not bad, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.10,0:01:01.13,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Earl Gray - it's one of my favorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.32,0:01:02.30,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Earl Grey?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.31,0:01:02.84,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.47,0:01:08.98,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,There are many different types of tea, all with different smells and tastes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.57,0:01:10.48,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:12.48,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.93,0:01:15.08,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I think it's very good,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:16.86,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,but what about you, Lain?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.57,0:01:19.65,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Drink a little bit and see if you like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:23.60,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,If it doesn't taste good, we can always make you something else, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.22,0:01:25.73,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Here you go.
